item.title: The Einstein Show - June 28, 2013
item.description: Hour 1 - Phone Calls, plus some 'Show and Tell' photos from the einsteinshow.net website, and Kidsville, USA slips in right before the end of the hour. Hour 2 - More with Kidsville, USA plus the Texas Belles, Donna, Kristine, and Ann Marie stop by for a visit. (See also Kristine & Friends Naked Around Town) Hour 3 - More with the Texas Belles plus a really big announcement from Einstein producer Mikey D.

item.title: The Einstein Show - May 28, 2013
item.description: Hour 1 - Dylan and Liza tell about the slumber party then went to on Friday. Sarah and Lisa join them on the phone. Also includes Loliwood shout-outs. Hour 2 - A game of 'Strip Poker' between some girls from rival schools. Hour 3 - Longtime Playdate model Michelle Wallace stops in and tells us some of the stories from her work in the magazine.

item.title: Jennifer's Camp-Out, Part 1
item.description: It's Jennifer's 8th birthday, and she has her friends over. On a warm summer evening, the girls soon get too warm...

item.title: An Orgy of Child Sex, Part 2
item.description: This is episode 43 in the Pedo Ring series. It can be read alone but would be best to read at least #41 first. All the episodes are loosely linked by the central premise of a pedo ring (see'summary of episodes' for full order). This one overran a bit because orgies are complex to describe! 35yo Sean, the host, is the central male character, stepdad to the extremely sexed 10yo Hannah.

item.title: An Orgy Of Child Sex, Part 1
item.description: This is episode 42 in the Ring series. It can be read alone but follows on directly from #40 & #41, which give the fuller setting. All the episodes are loosely linked by the central premise of a pedo ring (see'summary of episodes' for full order). Sean here is the central male character, stepdad to the extremely sexed 10yo Hannah. As the title suggests, tonight some of the other young girls in the ring are included.

item.title: Molly and the Babysitting Advert
item.description: A naive teenager falls prey to an evil paedophile. Initially being forced so comes to start to realise her place and enjoys it.

item.title: Miss Tide's After School Tying Up And Kissing Club
item.description: Sometimes a child doesn't always tell the truth about school and her mother has to go and find out from the teacher exactly what's going on, even if the truth isn't exactly what she expects to discover...

item.title: FiFi
item.description: A mature woman doesn't know what she will encounter when she goes to a club where little girls take advantage of women...

item.title: Driftwood
item.description: A lonely woman artist finds the greatest discovery of all washed up on a beach.

item.title: Matchmaker
item.description: A mother discovers her own daughter has plans for her to be happy...
